    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "ca554931-022b-4154-ac2a-136b9cd06a2a",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "静默意外 Quiet Accident",
        "Location": "LOCATION_GOLDEN_GECKO",
        "PublicId": "127972566632",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository fb2670e1-e16d-4e66-bb04-12e5d6e5bcb0).Image",
        "Description": "这次的委托来自一位家族破产的复仇者，目标是权杖塔灯光秀上的马库斯及其党羽。这些人曾靠欺诈手段谋夺委托人的家产，如今又想借这场盛会洗白过往、开展新的非法交易。客户非常在意现场与证据，你需要利用现场的灯光设备和观景设施制造意外，让他们在炫目的光影中永远沉默。\rThis mission is from a wronged client.\rYour targets are Marcus and his accomplices at the Scepter Tower light show.\rThey ruined the client’s family and now meet here for illegal deals.\rMake it look like accidents, and silence them all in the light show.",
        "GameVersion": "8.23.0.0",
        "IsPublished": true,
